metadata.description:
First NFT by the Midnite Artist.

I've been a photographer, videographer & artist for over 35+ years.  The NFT revolution is an exciting venture that no artist should miss out on!

This piece shows the struggle of Bitcoin's journey to the moon...  It is just within reach, but not not quite there...

The destination is a beautiful sight!

Limited Edition : Only 33 available

*Downloadable 4K version, upon purchase.

Thank you in advance for everyone that joins me on this journey!
